div.p:
This document describes the architecture
of the lungmen.akn platform in a visual way
with all the components and how they
interact with each other.

lungmen.akn serves as the home applications
cluster, providing media, life management,
and personal productivity services for
the homelab infrastructure.

g.title: Tailnet - Mesh VPN Network
UniFi Dream Machine Pro - Gateway & Network Controller
Mission-critical services cluster (SSO, Secrets, etc.)
Home Network Attached Storage (NAS)
Pocket-ID is an open-source identity and access management solution based only on passkeys.
OpenBao is an open-source, community-driven fork of Vault managed by the Linux Foundation.
MinIO is a high-performance, distributed object storage system.
Cert-Manager is a Kubernetes controller that automates the management and issuance of TLS certificates.
Cilium is a networking, observability, and security solution with an eBPF-based dataplane.
CloudNativePG is a comprehensive platform designed to seamlessly manage PostgreSQL databases within Kubernetes environments.
Envoy Gateway is a Kubernetes-native API Gateway powered by Envoy Proxy with support for Gateway API.
ExternalDNS configures DNS records automatically for exposed services.
External-Secret is a Kubernetes controller that allows you to use external secret management systems.
Longhorn is a lightweight, reliable, and powerful distributed block storage system for Kubernetes.
TailScale is a mesh VPN that makes it easy to connect your devices, wherever they are.
High-performance self-hosted photo and video management solution with mobile app support.
Volunteer-built media solution that puts you in control of your media.
Jellyseerr media request management stack with PostgreSQL backend
Personal finance app that helps you track your spending and save money.
Paperless document management stack with PostgreSQL backend and Redis cache
Atuin shell history sync stack with PostgreSQL backend
Linkding bookmarking stack with PostgreSQL backend
Free and open source software application for managing requests for media libraries.
PostgreSQL database backend for Jellyseerr, managed by CloudNative-PG operator with automated backups to S3.
Document management system to store, search and share documents.
PostgreSQL database backend for Paperless, managed by CloudNative-PG operator with automated backups to S3.
Redis cache for improved Paperless performance and background task processing.
Encrypted shell history sync, storing all your shell commands in one place.

Self-hosted bookmarking and link aggregation service.
